text.tspan: ImageNet Challenge: Top-5 accuracy of AI systems in labeling
The ImageNet Challenge has AI systems label images based on the main object in each image, such as a dog or car. Top-5
accuracy measures how often any one of the system's five most probable labels (out of 1000 possible labels) matches the target
Data source: Papers with Code, arXiv via AI Index Report (2022)
Note: Some systems were trained with extra data in addition to the base ImageNet training data.
